==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whoredom
<hw>Whore"dom</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>hordom</ets>; cf. Icel. <ets>h<?/rd<?/mr</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The practice of unlawful intercourse with the other
sex; fornication; lewdness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Script.)</fld> <def>The sin of worshiping idols;
idolatry.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>O Ephraim, thou committest <qex>whoredom</qex>, and Israel is
defiled; they will not . . . turn unto their God.</q> <rj><qau>Hos. v.
3, 4.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whoremaster</ent>⟦br⟧
